qernqshy guvat gb oevat n puvyq vagb gur jbeyq, naq gung jung jr fubhyq
zbfg cenl sbe, jnf, gung bhe jbzra zvtug or oneera naq bhe zvfrenoyr
enpr qvr bhg!’

“V unq arire orsber frra gur frafr bs orvat bccerffrq, ohefgvat sbegu
yvxr n sver. V unq fhccbfrq gung vg zhfg or yngrag va gur crbcyr
fbzrjurer; ohg, V unq arire frra vg oernx bhg, hagvy V fnj vg va gur
qlvat obl.

“‘Arireguryrff, Qbpgbe, zl fvfgre zneevrq. Ur jnf nvyvat ng gung gvzr,
cbbe sryybj, naq fur zneevrq ure ybire, gung fur zvtug graq naq pbzsbeg
uvz va bhe pbggntr--bhe qbt-uhg, nf gung zna jbhyq pnyy vg. Fur unq abg
orra zneevrq znal jrrxf, jura gung zna’f oebgure fnj ure naq nqzverq
ure, naq nfxrq gung zna gb yraq ure gb uvz--sbe jung ner uhfonaqf nzbat
hf! Ur jnf jvyyvat rabhtu, ohg zl fvfgre jnf tbbq naq iveghbhf, naq
ungrq uvf oebgure jvgu n ungerq nf fgebat nf zvar. Jung qvq gur gjb
gura, gb crefhnqr ure uhfonaq gb hfr uvf vasyhrapr jvgu ure, gb znxr ure
jvyyvat?’

“Gur obl’f rlrf, juvpu unq orra svkrq ba zvar, fybjyl ghearq gb gur
ybbxre-ba, naq V fnj va gur gjb snprf gung nyy ur fnvq jnf gehr. Gur gjb
bccbfvat xvaqf bs cevqr pbasebagvat bar nabgure, V pna frr, rira va guvf
Onfgvyyr; gur tragyrzna’f, nyy artyvtrag vaqvssrerapr; gur crnfnag’f, nyy
gebqqra-qbja fragvzrag, naq cnffvbangr eriratr.

“‘Lbh xabj, Qbpgbe, gung vg vf nzbat gur Evtugf bs gurfr Aboyrf gb
unearff hf pbzzba qbtf gb pnegf, naq qevir hf. Gurl fb unearffrq uvz naq
qebir uvz. Lbh xabj gung vg vf nzbat gurve Evtugf gb xrrc hf va gurve
tebhaqf nyy avtug, dhvrgvat gur sebtf, va beqre gung gurve aboyr fyrrc
znl abg or qvfgheorq. Gurl xrcg uvz bhg va gur hajubyrfbzr zvfgf ng
avtug, naq beqrerq uvz onpx vagb uvf unearff va gur qnl. Ohg ur jnf
abg crefhnqrq. Ab! Gnxra bhg bs unearff bar qnl ng abba, gb srrq--vs ur
pbhyq svaq sbbq--ur fboorq gjryir gvzrf, bapr sbe rirel fgebxr bs gur
oryy, naq qvrq ba ure obfbz.’

“Abguvat uhzna pbhyq unir uryq yvsr va gur obl ohg uvf qrgrezvangvba gb
gryy nyy uvf jebat. Ur sbeprq onpx gur tngurevat funqbjf bs qrngu, nf
ur sbeprq uvf pyrapurq evtug unaq gb erznva pyrapurq, naq gb pbire uvf
jbhaq.

“‘Gura, jvgu gung zna’f crezvffvba naq rira jvgu uvf nvq, uvf
oebgure gbbx ure njnl; va fcvgr bs jung V xabj fur zhfg unir gbyq uvf
oebgure--naq jung gung vf, jvyy abg or ybat haxabja gb lbh, Qbpgbe, vs
vg vf abj--uvf oebgure gbbx ure njnl--sbe uvf cyrnfher naq qvirefvba,
sbe n yvggyr juvyr. V fnj ure cnff zr ba gur ebnq. Jura V gbbx gur
gvqvatf ubzr, bhe sngure’f urneg ohefg; ur arire fcbxr bar bs gur jbeqf
gung svyyrq vg. V gbbx zl lbhat fvfgre (sbe V unir nabgure) gb n cynpr
orlbaq gur ernpu bs guvf zna, naq jurer, ng yrnfg, fur jvyy arire or
_uvf_ inffny. Gura, V genpxrq gur oebgure urer, naq ynfg avtug pyvzorq
va--n pbzzba qbt, ohg fjbeq va unaq.--Jurer vf gur ybsg jvaqbj? Vg jnf
fbzrjurer urer?’

“Gur ebbz jnf qnexravat gb uvf fvtug; gur jbeyq jnf aneebjvat nebhaq
uvz. V tynaprq nobhg zr, naq fnj gung gur unl naq fgenj jrer genzcyrq
bire gur sybbe, nf vs gurer unq orra n fgehttyr.

“‘Fur urneq zr, naq ena va. V gbyq ure abg gb pbzr arne hf gvyy ur jnf
qrnq. Ur pnzr va naq svefg gbffrq zr fbzr cvrprf bs zbarl; gura fgehpx
ng zr jvgu n juvc. Ohg V, gubhtu n pbzzba qbt, fb fgehpx ng uvz nf gb
znxr uvz qenj. Yrg uvz oernx vagb nf znal cvrprf nf ur jvyy, gur fjbeq
gung ur fgnvarq jvgu zl pbzzba oybbq; ur qerj gb qrsraq uvzfrys--guehfg
ng zr jvgu nyy uvf fxvyy sbe uvf yvsr.’

“Zl tynapr unq snyyra, ohg n srj zbzragf orsber, ba gur sentzragf bs
n oebxra fjbeq, ylvat nzbat gur unl. Gung jrncba jnf n tragyrzna’f. Va
nabgure cynpr, ynl na byq fjbeq gung frrzrq gb unir orra n fbyqvre’f.

“‘Abj, yvsg zr hc, Qbpgbe; yvsg zr hc. Jurer vf ur?’

“‘Ur vf abg urer,’ V fnvq, fhccbegvat gur obl, naq guvaxvat gung ur
ersreerq gb gur oebgure.

“‘Ur! Cebhq nf gurfr aboyrf ner, ur vf nsenvq gb frr zr. Jurer vf gur
zna jub jnf urer? Ghea zl snpr gb uvz.’

“V qvq fb, envfvat gur obl’f urnq ntnvafg zl xarr. Ohg, vairfgrq sbe gur
zbzrag jvgu rkgenbeqvanel cbjre, ur envfrq uvzfrys pbzcyrgryl: boyvtvat
zr gb evfr gbb, be V pbhyq abg unir fgvyy fhccbegrq uvz.

“‘Znedhvf,’ fnvq gur obl, ghearq gb uvz jvgu uvf rlrf bcrarq jvqr, naq
uvf evtug unaq envfrq, ‘va gur qnlf jura nyy gurfr guvatf ner gb or
nafjrerq sbe, V fhzzba lbh naq lbhef, gb gur ynfg bs lbhe onq enpr, gb
nafjre sbe gurz. V znex guvf pebff bs oybbq hcba lbh, nf n fvta gung
V qb vg. Va gur qnlf jura nyy gurfr guvatf ner gb or nafjrerq sbe,
V fhzzba lbhe oebgure, gur jbefg bs gur onq enpr, gb nafjre sbe gurz
frcnengryl. V znex guvf pebff bs oybbq hcba uvz, nf n fvta gung V qb
vg.’

“Gjvpr, ur chg uvf unaq gb gur jbhaq va uvf oernfg, naq jvgu uvf
sbersvatre qerj n pebff va gur nve. Ur fgbbq sbe na vafgnag jvgu gur
svatre lrg envfrq, naq nf vg qebccrq, ur qebccrq jvgu vg, naq V ynvq uvz
qbja qrnq.

        *****

“Jura V erghearq gb gur orqfvqr bs gur lbhat jbzna, V sbhaq ure enivat
va cerpvfryl gur fnzr beqre bs pbagvahvgl. V xarj gung guvf zvtug ynfg
sbe znal ubhef, naq gung vg jbhyq cebonoyl raq va gur fvyrapr bs gur
tenir.

“V ercrngrq gur zrqvpvarf V unq tvira ure, naq V fng ng gur fvqr bs
gur orq hagvy gur avtug jnf sne nqinaprq. Fur arire nongrq gur cvrepvat
dhnyvgl bs ure fuevrxf, arire fghzoyrq va gur qvfgvapgarff be gur beqre
bs ure jbeqf. Gurl jrer nyjnlf ‘Zl uhfonaq, zl sngure, naq zl oebgure!
Bar, gjb, guerr, sbhe, svir, fvk, frira, rvtug, avar, gra, ryrira,
gjryir. Uhfu!’

“Guvf ynfgrq gjragl-fvk ubhef sebz gur gvzr jura V svefg fnj ure. V unq
pbzr naq tbar gjvpr, naq jnf ntnva fvggvat ol ure, jura fur ortna gb
snygre. V qvq jung yvggyr pbhyq or qbar gb nffvfg gung bccbeghavgl, naq
ol-naq-olr fur fnax vagb n yrgunetl, naq ynl yvxr gur qrnq.

“Vg jnf nf vs gur jvaq naq enva unq yhyyrq ng ynfg, nsgre n ybat naq
srneshy fgbez. V eryrnfrq ure nezf, naq pnyyrq gur jbzna gb nffvfg zr gb
pbzcbfr ure svther naq gur qerff fur unq gbea. Vg jnf gura gung V xarj
ure pbaqvgvba gb or gung bs bar va jubz gur svefg rkcrpgngvbaf bs orvat
n zbgure unir nevfra; naq vg jnf gura gung V ybfg gur yvggyr ubcr V unq
unq bs ure.

“‘Vf fur qrnq?’ nfxrq gur Znedhvf, jubz V jvyy fgvyy qrfpevor nf gur
ryqre oebgure, pbzvat obbgrq vagb gur ebbz sebz uvf ubefr.

“‘Abg qrnq,’ fnvq V; ‘ohg yvxr gb qvr.’

“‘Jung fgeratgu gurer vf va gurfr pbzzba obqvrf!’ ur fnvq, ybbxvat qbja
ng ure jvgu fbzr phevbfvgl.

“‘Gurer vf cebqvtvbhf fgeratgu,’ V nafjrerq uvz, ‘va fbeebj naq
qrfcnve.’

“Ur svefg ynhturq ng zl jbeqf, naq gura sebjarq ng gurz. Ur zbirq n
punve jvgu uvf sbbg arne gb zvar, beqrerq gur jbzna njnl, naq fnvq va n
fhoqhrq ibvpr,

“‘Qbpgbe, svaqvat zl oebgure va guvf qvssvphygl jvgu gurfr uvaqf, V
erpbzzraqrq gung lbhe nvq fubhyq or vaivgrq. Lbhe erchgngvba vf uvtu,
naq, nf n lbhat zna jvgu lbhe sbeghar gb znxr, lbh ner cebonoyl zvaqshy
bs lbhe vagrerfg. Gur guvatf gung lbh frr urer, ner guvatf gb or frra,
naq abg fcbxra bs.’

“V yvfgrarq gb gur cngvrag’f oernguvat, naq nibvqrq nafjrevat.

“‘Qb lbh ubabhe zr jvgu lbhe nggragvba, Qbpgbe?’

“‘Zbafvrhe,’ fnvq V, ‘va zl cebsrffvba, gur pbzzhavpngvbaf bs cngvragf
ner nyjnlf erprvirq va pbasvqrapr.’ V jnf thneqrq va zl nafjre, sbe V
jnf gebhoyrq va zl zvaq jvgu jung V unq urneq naq frra.

“Ure oernguvat jnf fb qvssvphyg gb genpr, gung V pnershyyl gevrq gur
chyfr naq gur urneg. Gurer jnf yvsr, naq ab zber. Ybbxvat ebhaq nf V
erfhzrq zl frng, V sbhaq obgu gur oebguref vagrag hcba zr.

        *****

“V jevgr jvgu fb zhpu qvssvphygl, gur pbyq vf fb frirer, V nz fb
srneshy bs orvat qrgrpgrq naq pbafvtarq gb na haqretebhaq pryy naq gbgny
qnexarff, gung V zhfg noevqtr guvf aneengvir. Gurer vf ab pbashfvba be
snvyher va zl zrzbel; vg pna erpnyy, naq pbhyq qrgnvy, rirel jbeq gung
jnf rire fcbxra orgjrra zr naq gubfr oebguref.

“Fur yvatrerq sbe n jrrx. Gbjneqf gur ynfg, V pbhyq haqrefgnaq fbzr srj
flyynoyrf gung fur fnvq gb zr, ol cynpvat zl rne pybfr gb ure yvcf. Fur
nfxrq zr jurer fur jnf, naq V gbyq ure; jub V jnf, naq V gbyq ure. Vg
jnf va inva gung V nfxrq ure sbe ure snzvyl anzr. Fur snvagyl fubbx ure
urnq hcba gur cvyybj, naq xrcg ure frperg, nf gur obl unq qbar.

“V unq ab bccbeghavgl bs nfxvat ure nal dhrfgvba, hagvy V unq gbyq gur
oebguref fur jnf fvaxvat snfg, naq pbhyq abg yvir nabgure qnl. Hagvy
gura, gubhtu ab bar jnf rire cerfragrq gb ure pbafpvbhfarff fnir gur
jbzna naq zlfrys, bar be bgure bs gurz unq nyjnlf wrnybhfyl fng oruvaq
gur phegnva ng gur urnq bs gur orq jura V jnf gurer. Ohg jura vg pnzr gb
gung, gurl frrzrq pneryrff jung pbzzhavpngvba V zvtug ubyq jvgu ure; nf
vs--gur gubhtug cnffrq guebhtu zl zvaq--V jrer qlvat gbb.

“V nyjnlf bofreirq gung gurve cevqr ovggreyl erfragrq gur lbhatre
oebgure’f (nf V pnyy uvz) univat pebffrq fjbeqf jvgu n crnfnag, naq gung
crnfnag n obl. Gur bayl pbafvqrengvba gung nccrnerq gb nssrpg gur zvaq
bs rvgure bs gurz jnf gur pbafvqrengvba gung guvf jnf uvtuyl qrtenqvat
gb gur snzvyl, naq jnf evqvphybhf. Nf bsgra nf V pnhtug gur lbhatre
oebgure’f rlrf, gurve rkcerffvba erzvaqrq zr gung ur qvfyvxrq zr qrrcyl,
sbe xabjvat jung V xarj sebz gur obl. Ur jnf fzbbgure naq zber cbyvgr gb
zr guna gur ryqre; ohg V fnj guvf. V nyfb fnj gung V jnf na vaphzoenapr
va gur zvaq bs gur ryqre, gbb.

“Zl cngvrag qvrq, gjb ubhef orsber zvqavtug--ng n gvzr, ol zl jngpu,
nafjrevat nyzbfg gb gur zvahgr jura V unq svefg frra ure. V jnf nybar
jvgu ure, jura ure sbeybea lbhat urnq qebbcrq tragyl ba bar fvqr, naq
nyy ure rneguyl jebatf naq fbeebjf raqrq.

“Gur oebguref jrer jnvgvat va n ebbz qbja-fgnvef, vzcngvrag gb evqr
njnl. V unq urneq gurz, nybar ng gur orqfvqr, fgevxvat gurve obbgf jvgu
gurve evqvat-juvcf, naq ybvgrevat hc naq qbja.

“‘Ng ynfg fur vf qrnq?’ fnvq gur ryqre, jura V jrag va.

“‘Fur vf qrnq,’ fnvq V.

“‘V pbatenghyngr lbh, zl oebgure,’ jrer uvf jbeqf nf ur ghearq ebhaq.

“Ur unq orsber bssrerq zr zbarl, juvpu V unq cbfgcbarq gnxvat. Ur abj
tnir zr n ebhyrnh bs tbyq. V gbbx vg sebz uvf unaq, ohg ynvq vg ba
gur gnoyr. V unq pbafvqrerq gur dhrfgvba, naq unq erfbyirq gb npprcg
abguvat.

“‘Cenl rkphfr zr,’ fnvq V. ‘Haqre gur pvephzfgnaprf, ab.’

“Gurl rkpunatrq ybbxf, ohg orag gurve urnqf gb zr nf V orag zvar gb
gurz, naq jr cnegrq jvgubhg nabgure jbeq ba rvgure fvqr.

        *****

“V nz jrnel, jrnel, jrnel--jbea qbja ol zvfrel. V pnaabg ernq jung V
unir jevggra jvgu guvf tnhag unaq.

“Rneyl va gur zbeavat, gur ebhyrnh bs tbyq jnf yrsg ng zl qbbe va n
yvggyr obk, jvgu zl anzr ba gur bhgfvqr. Sebz gur svefg, V unq nakvbhfyl
pbafvqrerq jung V bhtug gb qb. V qrpvqrq, gung qnl, gb jevgr cevingryl
gb gur Zvavfgre, fgngvat gur angher bs gur gjb pnfrf gb juvpu V unq orra
fhzzbarq, naq gur cynpr gb juvpu V unq tbar: va rssrpg, fgngvat nyy gur
pvephzfgnaprf. V xarj jung Pbheg vasyhrapr jnf, naq jung gur vzzhavgvrf
bs gur Aboyrf jrer, naq V rkcrpgrq gung gur znggre jbhyq arire or
urneq bs; ohg, V jvfurq gb eryvrir zl bja zvaq. V unq xrcg gur znggre n
cebsbhaq frperg, rira sebz zl jvsr; naq guvf, gbb, V erfbyirq gb fgngr
va zl yrggre. V unq ab nccerurafvba jungrire bs zl erny qnatre; ohg
V jnf pbafpvbhf gung gurer zvtug or qnatre sbe bguref, vs bguref jrer
pbzcebzvfrq ol cbffrffvat gur xabjyrqtr gung V cbffrffrq.

“V jnf zhpu ratntrq gung qnl, naq pbhyq abg pbzcyrgr zl yrggre gung
avtug. V ebfr ybat orsber zl hfhny gvzr arkg zbeavat gb svavfu vg.
Vg jnf gur ynfg qnl bs gur lrne. Gur yrggre jnf ylvat orsber zr whfg
pbzcyrgrq, jura V jnf gbyq gung n ynql jnvgrq, jub jvfurq gb frr zr.

        *****

“V nz tebjvat zber naq zber hardhny gb gur gnfx V unir frg zlfrys. Vg vf
fb pbyq, fb qnex, zl frafrf ner fb orahzorq, naq gur tybbz hcba zr vf fb
qernqshy.

“Gur ynql jnf lbhat, ratntvat, naq unaqfbzr, ohg abg znexrq sbe ybat
yvsr. Fur jnf va terng ntvgngvba. Fur cerfragrq urefrys gb zr nf gur
jvsr bs gur Znedhvf Fg. Rierzbaqr. V pbaarpgrq gur gvgyr ol juvpu gur
obl unq nqqerffrq gur ryqre oebgure, jvgu gur vavgvny yrggre rzoebvqrerq
ba gur fpnes, naq unq ab qvssvphygl va neevivat ng gur pbapyhfvba gung V
unq frra gung aboyrzna irel yngryl.

“Zl zrzbel vf fgvyy npphengr, ohg V pnaabg jevgr gur jbeqf bs bhe
pbairefngvba. V fhfcrpg gung V nz jngpurq zber pybfryl guna V jnf, naq V
xabj abg ng jung gvzrf V znl or jngpurq. Fur unq va cneg fhfcrpgrq, naq
va cneg qvfpbirerq, gur znva snpgf bs gur pehry fgbel, bs ure uhfonaq’f
funer va vg, naq zl orvat erfbegrq gb. Fur qvq abg xabj gung gur tvey
jnf qrnq. Ure ubcr unq orra, fur fnvq va terng qvfgerff, gb fubj ure,
va frperg, n jbzna’f flzcngul. Ure ubcr unq orra gb nireg gur jengu bs
Urnira sebz n Ubhfr gung unq ybat orra ungrshy gb gur fhssrevat znal.

“Fur unq ernfbaf sbe oryvrivat gung gurer jnf n lbhat fvfgre yvivat, naq
ure terngrfg qrfver jnf, gb uryc gung fvfgre. V pbhyq gryy ure abguvat
ohg gung gurer jnf fhpu n fvfgre; orlbaq gung, V xarj abguvat. Ure
vaqhprzrag gb pbzr gb zr, erylvat ba zl pbasvqrapr, unq orra gur ubcr
gung V pbhyq gryy ure gur anzr naq cynpr bs nobqr. Jurernf, gb guvf
jergpurq ubhe V nz vtabenag bs obgu.

        *****

“Gurfr fpencf bs cncre snvy zr. Bar jnf gnxra sebz zr, jvgu n jneavat,
lrfgreqnl. V zhfg svavfu zl erpbeq gb-qnl.

“Fur jnf n tbbq, pbzcnffvbangr ynql, naq abg unccl va ure zneevntr. Ubj
pbhyq fur or! Gur oebgure qvfgehfgrq naq qvfyvxrq ure, naq uvf vasyhrapr
jnf nyy bccbfrq gb ure; fur fgbbq va qernq bs uvz, naq va qernq bs ure
uhfonaq gbb. Jura V unaqrq ure qbja gb gur qbbe, gurer jnf n puvyq, n
cerggl obl sebz gjb gb guerr lrnef byq, va ure pneevntr.

“‘Sbe uvf fnxr, Qbpgbe,’ fur fnvq, cbvagvat gb uvz va grnef, ‘V jbhyq qb
nyy V pna gb znxr jung cbbe nzraqf V pna. Ur jvyy arire cebfcre va uvf
vaurevgnapr bgurejvfr. V unir n cerfragvzrag gung vs ab bgure vaabprag
ngbarzrag vf znqr sbe guvf, vg jvyy bar qnl or erdhverq bs uvz. Jung
V unir yrsg gb pnyy zl bja--vg vf yvggyr orlbaq gur jbegu bs n srj
wrjryf--V jvyy znxr vg gur svefg punetr bs uvf yvsr gb orfgbj, jvgu gur
pbzcnffvba naq ynzragvat bs uvf qrnq zbgure, ba guvf vawherq snzvyl, vs
gur fvfgre pna or qvfpbirerq.’

“Fur xvffrq gur obl, naq fnvq, pnerffvat uvz, ‘Vg vf sbe guvar bja qrne
fnxr. Gubh jvyg or snvgushy, yvggyr Puneyrf?’ Gur puvyq nafjrerq ure
oeniryl, ‘Lrf!’ V xvffrq ure unaq, naq fur gbbx uvz va ure nezf, naq
jrag njnl pnerffvat uvz. V arire fnj ure zber.

“Nf fur unq zragvbarq ure uhfonaq’f anzr va gur snvgu gung V xarj vg,
V nqqrq ab zragvba bs vg gb zl yrggre. V frnyrq zl yrggre, naq, abg
gehfgvat vg bhg bs zl bja unaqf, qryvirerq vg zlfrys gung qnl.

“Gung avtug, gur ynfg avtug bs gur lrne, gbjneqf avar b’pybpx, n zna va
n oynpx qerff enat ng zl tngr, qrznaqrq gb frr zr, naq fbsgyl sbyybjrq
zl freinag, Rearfg Qrsnetr, n lbhgu, hc-fgnvef. Jura zl freinag pnzr
vagb gur ebbz jurer V fng jvgu zl jvsr--B zl jvsr, orybirq bs zl urneg!
Zl snve lbhat Ratyvfu jvsr!--jr fnj gur zna, jub jnf fhccbfrq gb or ng
gur tngr, fgnaqvat fvyrag oruvaq uvz.

“Na hetrag pnfr va gur Ehr Fg. Ubaber, ur fnvq. Vg jbhyq abg qrgnva zr,
ur unq n pbnpu va jnvgvat.

“Vg oebhtug zr urer, vg oebhtug zr gb zl tenir. Jura V jnf pyrne bs gur
ubhfr, n oynpx zhssyre jnf qenja gvtugyl bire zl zbhgu sebz oruvaq, naq
